&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Portfolio Manager will play a critical role within the Capital Markets team, overseeing ongoing compliance, reporting, and operational obligations across the Company’s portfolio of financed projects. This individual will act as a central point of ownership and coordination between internal teams (finance, development, construction, operations, legal) and external stakeholders (lenders, tax equity investors, insurers, and advisors) to ensure all financing and project-level requirements are met.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is ideal for a detail-oriented finance professional who thrives at the intersection of capital markets, operations, and compliance in a fast-growing infrastructure platform.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Financing Compliance &amp;amp; Reporting&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead compliance with all covenants, reporting obligations, and deliverables under corporate credit facilities, project-level debt, and tax equity agreements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the preparation and timely delivery of periodic reports (monthly, quarterly, annual), including financial statements, operating reports, compliance certificates, and investor updates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track key dates, milestones, and obligations across all financing agreements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with NineDot colleagues to gather required inputs from finance, development, construction, operations, and legal teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Construction Financing &amp;amp; Capital Deployment&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage and execute draw requests under construction loan facilities, including lender coordination and documentation review&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee the process of adding new distributed energy projects into existing financing structures (construction debt and tax equity), including satisfaction of conditions precedent&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with internal company stakeholders to ensure readiness for funding milestones&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain detailed draw schedules and funding trackers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
