&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Summary:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Senior Accountant at NineDot Energy, you’ll play a key role in building the financial foundation of one of New York’s fastest-growing clean energy developers. You’ll own core accounting processes, ensure accuracy across financial reporting, and help strengthen internal controls - all while supporting the company’s mission to create a more resilient, sustainable energy future. This is a high-visibility role with room to grow, offering the chance to shape accounting practices in a collaborative, fast-paced environment.&lt;/p&gt;
